1
00:00:05,767 --> 00:00:08,632
Child, welcome home.

2
00:00:08,733 --> 00:00:13,066
Human, you truly thought you could hide from me?

3
00:00:13,333 --> 00:00:15,766
Human Luo Feng pays respects
to the Starry Sky Ancestor.

4
00:00:16,233 --> 00:00:18,599
Within a hundred Epochs,
if you succeed,

5
00:00:18,667 --> 00:00:22,366
I shall bestow upon you
the ultimate treasure set of the Beast God lineage.

6
00:00:22,700 --> 00:00:25,566
May I ask, what requirement
did Teacher Zuo Shan Ke leave?

7
00:00:25,767 --> 00:00:27,432
Defeat me.

8
00:00:28,667 --> 00:00:30,599
As long as you continue cultivating
the Nine Calamity Secret Codex,

9
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:33,332
allowing the Golden Horned Beast
to reach the Perfect Gene level,

10
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:35,166
I, for the Universe...

11
00:00:35,167 --> 00:00:35,432
I, for the Universe...

12
00:00:53,900 --> 00:00:56,766
This is a Miniature Universe.

13
00:00:59,633 --> 00:01:01,466
Previously, fearing immense consumption,

14
00:01:01,467 --> 00:01:04,032
I never utilized this innate
talent secret method after acquiring it.

15
00:01:04,933 --> 00:01:05,966
It is indeed astonishing.

16
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:09,532
How profound and wondrous.

17
00:01:10,333 --> 00:01:12,332
I can absolutely control
this Miniature Universe,

18
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:14,299
suppressing enemies at will,

19
00:01:14,900 --> 00:01:15,932
enhancing myself...

20
00:01:16,433 --> 00:01:20,132
And with just a single thought, I can destroy this universe.

21
00:01:21,100 --> 00:01:23,766
This secret method is far too heaven-defying.

22
00:01:25,233 --> 00:01:26,233
Babata.

23
00:01:28,100 --> 00:01:29,232
You aren't...

24
00:01:30,467 --> 00:01:32,266
in the Beast God Realm?

25
00:01:45,367 --> 00:01:46,232
Truly beautiful.

26
00:01:46,667 --> 00:01:50,299
These secret pattern diagrams
are the operational laws
of the entire Miniature Universe.

27
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:52,966
Vast, complex, and precise.

28
00:01:54,700 --> 00:01:55,700
This is...

29
00:01:57,833 --> 00:02:00,266
The secret patterns from the
sixty-four Beast God statues.

30
00:02:05,733 --> 00:02:09,966
So these seemingly random tangles
of billions of Law threads

31
00:02:10,233 --> 00:02:13,732
are actually composed of
small secret patterns from those statues.

32
00:02:14,433 --> 00:02:15,766
This is unbelievable.

33
00:02:17,233 --> 00:02:19,032
Could it be that constructing
ultimate techniques

34
00:02:19,467 --> 00:02:21,166
actually follows discernible laws?

35
00:02:24,733 --> 00:02:29,166
The Great Annihilation Era is
an unfathomably distant time,
known by few.

36
00:02:30,167 --> 00:02:31,266
Before the Great Annihilation,

37
00:02:31,267 --> 00:02:35,666
there existed a cultivation method
using the sixty-four secret patterns
as basic elements.

38
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:48,399
What use is constantly
sketching secret patterns?

39
00:02:48,500 --> 00:02:50,399
It has been over ten thousand years.

40
00:02:50,733 --> 00:02:56,132
The most crucial and elusive part
of the Beast God Path
is the Heart of the Beast God.

41
00:02:56,533 --> 00:03:01,066
One must comprehend the Heart
to truly incarnate as a Beast God.

42
00:03:01,367 --> 00:03:03,332
He has strayed onto the wrong path.

43
00:03:03,900 --> 00:03:08,266
The Eight Great Beast Gods
are embodiments of fused laws.

44
00:03:08,433 --> 00:03:13,666
And the sixty-four secret patterns
are the perfect interpretation of the natural Eight Beast Gods.

45
00:03:13,833 --> 00:03:18,566
The most pinnacle secret techniques
can all be decomposed into sixty-four secret patterns.

46
00:03:19,100 --> 00:03:21,232
Luo Feng's Nine Nether Avatar

47
00:03:21,233 --> 00:03:24,566
reached the Perfect Gene level
even before reaching Immortality.

48
00:03:24,733 --> 00:03:27,799
He must have received the gift
of the strongest talent technique.

49
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:32,966
If Luo Feng notices the connection
between his talent technique and the sixty-four secret patterns,

50
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:35,599
he won't need to understand
the underlying principles;

51
00:03:35,667 --> 00:03:38,832
he only needs to firmly memorize
the structure of each secret pattern,

52
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:43,166
then reference the structure
of the talent technique he received
to create...

53
00:03:43,567 --> 00:03:45,099
Once successful,

54
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:49,532
he can create a simplified version
of the strongest talent technique.

55
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:51,732
It is not impossible.

56
00:04:11,500 --> 00:04:13,732
Restoring all secret patterns
is too difficult for now.

57
00:04:14,067 --> 00:04:17,666
For now, focus on studying
the eight secret patterns
of the Gold Beast God.

58
00:05:54,333 --> 00:05:55,166
I am...

59
00:05:56,167 --> 00:05:57,167
the Beast God.

60
00:05:58,633 --> 00:05:59,899
I actually lost focus for a moment.

61
00:06:00,267 --> 00:06:01,632
What a curious sensation.

62
00:06:01,667 --> 00:06:04,032
Is this what Zhuangzi dreaming of butterflies feels like?

63
00:06:06,433 --> 00:06:07,433
What?

64
00:06:07,700 --> 00:06:09,966
The ultimate bottleneck
of the Beast God Path—

65
00:06:10,033 --> 00:06:12,766
the most elusive and hardest-to-obtain
Heart of the Beast God—

66
00:06:12,967 --> 00:06:14,932
he actually mastered it just like that?

67
00:06:17,067 --> 00:06:19,732
But even so, it doesn't mean...

68
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,199
Wait, that is...

69
00:06:45,333 --> 00:06:47,232
It actually succeeded.

70
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:50,032
A pinnacle ultimate technique
at the level of a Universe Master.

71
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,832
Starry Sky Ancestor.

72
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:57,232
I, Luo Feng, challenge you.

73
00:07:22,300 --> 00:07:23,932
Challenging me?

74
00:07:25,133 --> 00:07:26,332
With what weapon?

75
00:07:28,833 --> 00:07:30,299
You use your hands.

76
00:07:30,433 --> 00:07:33,432
Shall I also use these human hands?

77
00:07:34,133 --> 00:07:35,133
Hands.

78
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:39,832
You comprehended the Heart of the Beast God,
yet you cannot use hands as weapons?

79
00:07:43,700 --> 00:07:44,766
Make your move.

80
00:07:44,790 --> 00:09:01,190
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

81
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,332
He actually won.

82
00:10:10,033 --> 00:10:12,399
Even if suppressed to the same
Divine Body level,

83
00:10:12,667 --> 00:10:13,966
that is still the Ancestor!

84
00:10:14,533 --> 00:10:15,966
This feels unreal.

85
00:10:16,533 --> 00:10:17,632
Thank you, Starry Sky Ancestor.

86
00:10:18,033 --> 00:10:19,799
From beginning to end,
you were purely defending.

87
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,566
That is why I was lucky enough to win.

88
00:10:22,267 --> 00:10:23,766
No need for modesty.

89
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:27,499
I already deployed the highest defensive measures
of a Universe Master.

90
00:10:28,133 --> 00:10:31,532
If I had attacked with full force from the start,
I might have defeated you.

91
00:10:31,900 --> 00:10:35,699
But if you continued challenging me,
you would eventually triumph.

92
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:39,932
Since that is the case,
there is no need to waste time.

93
00:10:41,533 --> 00:10:43,232
Well done, Luo Feng.

94
00:10:44,933 --> 00:10:47,566
After one hundred eighty million years,

95
00:10:47,700 --> 00:10:50,866
you have finally been completely
reborn and remolded.

96
00:10:51,300 --> 00:10:55,666
In the past, you relied on
supreme treasures and secret codes to stand among the strong.

97
00:10:56,167 --> 00:10:59,632
Now, you have accumulated
truly deep and substantial power.

98
00:11:01,667 --> 00:11:05,066
In the coming cultivation,
you should be able to achieve a breakthrough in one breath.

99
00:11:05,433 --> 00:11:11,132
Probably only crossing the threshold
of Universe Master will pose a slight obstruction.

100
00:11:12,433 --> 00:11:14,199
Zuo Shan Ke, don't get cocky.

101
00:11:14,500 --> 00:11:17,966
Those are your disciple's achievements,
not yours.

102
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,732
Furthermore, his success...

103
00:11:19,833 --> 00:11:23,766
who can say it isn't because of
the Golden Horned Beast avatar?

104
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:28,332
Whose credit it is doesn't matter.

105
00:11:29,167 --> 00:11:31,332
But don't forget the bet.

106
00:11:31,967 --> 00:11:36,366
You are the Starry Sky Ancestor,
one of the nine superpowers of the universe.

107
00:11:36,533 --> 00:11:37,766
You wouldn't be stingy, would you?

108
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:40,832
I'm still waiting for that
Treasure Set of yours.

109
00:11:41,300 --> 00:11:44,766
If I lose, I lose. I naturally
keep my word.

110
00:11:47,767 --> 00:11:49,099
Luo Feng, look.

111
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:59,066
This is the Treasure Set—Beast God Armor.

112
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:02,199
Composed of five hundred
and twenty-six Treasures.

113
00:12:03,467 --> 00:12:04,699
Five hundred and twenty-six!

114
00:12:05,300 --> 00:12:07,699
Even Chaos City Lord's
teacher's 'River of Ten Thousand Treasures'

115
00:12:07,967 --> 00:12:09,966
was composed of only a thousand treasures.

116
00:12:22,460 --> 00:12:26,732
Within the set, there are four
High-Level Treasures and one
Pinnacle Treasure.

117
00:12:26,833 --> 00:12:28,932
The rest are ordinary Treasures.

118
00:12:29,433 --> 00:12:33,799
Its fangs, horn, scales, and body
can be used separately.

119
00:12:34,400 --> 00:12:38,466
Combined, they merge into one,
possessing world-shaking might.

120
00:12:39,467 --> 00:12:44,232
It is absolutely the most suitable
equipment for powerhouses cultivating the Beast God Path.

121
00:12:52,667 --> 00:12:54,066
It's too wonderful.

122
00:13:36,733 --> 00:13:39,766
We have disturbed you for years;
it is time we left.

123
00:13:40,267 --> 00:13:41,267
Luo Feng.

124
00:13:49,300 --> 00:13:50,799
Don't be in such a rush.

125
00:13:51,533 --> 00:13:52,966
There is one more thing.

126
00:13:54,700 --> 00:13:56,099
It has nothing to do with you.

127
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:09,799
Many thanks, Ancestor,
for the gift.

128
00:14:09,867 --> 00:14:14,199
Luo Feng, my Starry Sky Beast Alliance
possesses superior resources

129
00:14:14,267 --> 00:14:15,532
and better prospects for growth.

130
00:14:16,333 --> 00:14:19,299
Do you have any thoughts of leaving
the Human Race?

131
00:14:19,367 --> 00:14:20,367
No.

132
00:14:24,633 --> 00:14:25,666
As I thought.

133
00:14:26,033 --> 00:14:29,232
You haven't cultivated for long;
your kin and friends are all here.

134
00:14:29,400 --> 00:14:31,266
Your heart still holds attachments.

135
00:14:36,967 --> 00:14:37,967
How about this:

136
00:14:39,033 --> 00:14:42,999
Let your Golden Horned Beast avatar
join my Starry Sky Beast Alliance.

137
00:14:43,367 --> 00:14:45,899
It won't affect your status
as a human.

138
00:14:46,067 --> 00:14:47,932
And you gain another faction
as your backing.

139
00:14:48,067 --> 00:14:49,199
What's not good about that?

140
00:14:49,633 --> 00:14:52,166
But correspondingly, you bear
more responsibility.

141
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:57,266
The Alliance aids you, so naturally,
you must shoulder responsibilities.

142
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:03,532
No problem. I can bear the
responsibility.

143
00:15:22,267 --> 00:15:26,632
Starry Sky Ancestor, seeing your
expression, the recruitment worked.

144
00:15:27,567 --> 00:15:29,866
Is there any benefit for my disciple?

145
00:15:30,133 --> 00:15:33,832
Doesn't the clan bestow Treasures
upon the rise of new talents?

146
00:15:34,533 --> 00:15:35,599
Previously...

147
00:15:35,633 --> 00:15:39,532
Don't tell me the Beast God Armor
counts—that was from a bet.

148
00:15:39,867 --> 00:15:43,266
It wasn't gifted by the Alliance
to Luo Feng.

149
00:15:44,467 --> 00:15:45,766
Fine, fine, fine.

150
00:15:45,867 --> 00:15:48,532
You old fellow really know how
to bargain.

151
00:15:49,533 --> 00:15:54,399
My disciple joining the Alliance
is a blessing for your Starry
Sky Beasts.

152
00:15:54,933 --> 00:15:58,166
You, as a teacher, weren't even
this generous.

153
00:15:58,567 --> 00:16:02,799
Rest assured, what I give will be
better than yours.

154
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:08,299
Then I shall bestow upon his human
true body a High-Level Treasure close-combat weapon.

155
00:16:15,400 --> 00:16:16,632
You old rascal.

156
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:33,666
After obtaining the 'Zhan Ye Blade'
from Starry Sky Ancestor,

157
00:16:33,800 --> 00:16:36,066
my teacher and I returned to
the Original Universe.

158
00:16:42,267 --> 00:16:44,566
If you need to contact me,

159
00:16:44,700 --> 00:16:49,766
just transmit a message via
consciousness entering this; I will receive it.

160
00:16:51,133 --> 00:16:52,932
The recovery of universal
operating rules

161
00:16:53,467 --> 00:16:55,632
allowed my Golden Horned Beast
to rapidly transform.

162
00:16:56,367 --> 00:16:59,232
Leaping in a short time to become
a Perfect Divine Body.

163
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:15,632
Everything is ready. It is time
to return to the Original Stars.

164
00:17:17,267 --> 00:17:19,666
Say whatever, he insists on going
to the Original Stars.

165
00:17:19,667 --> 00:17:22,532
Two epochs have passed, and he
hasn't entered even once.

166
00:17:22,700 --> 00:17:24,599
He just doesn't dare to go in,
right?

167
00:17:24,933 --> 00:17:26,932
He has too many Treasures and
too much fame.

168
00:17:27,300 --> 00:17:29,932
The moment he enters, he will
definitely be besieged by all factions.

169
00:17:30,100 --> 00:17:31,366
He isn't stupid.

170
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:35,066
Entering the Original Stars
as a human

171
00:17:35,167 --> 00:17:37,232
will surely lead to even
more brutal slaughter.

172
00:17:37,600 --> 00:17:39,632
The outside world is spreading
rumors that I am afraid.

173
00:17:39,633 --> 00:17:40,166
The outskirts of the
Original Stars...

174
00:17:40,367 --> 00:17:41,367
However,

175
00:17:42,133 --> 00:17:43,799
that is precisely what I desire.

176
00:17:43,823 --> 00:18:25,423
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

